comments: [Observable in enhanced video] Oubre Jr. (PHX) splits his feet at the start of his dribble.
Green (GSW) makes contact with Oubre Jr.'s (PHX) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Holmes (PHX) makes contact to McKinnie's (GSW) arm during his shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
Johnson (PHX) establishes himself in the path of Thompson (GSW) and makes contact with his side during the pick but he is able to defend through the play.
Ayton (PHX) establishes himself in a legal position in the path of Thompson (GSW) and gives him room to avoid contact.
Curry (GSW) cleanly dislodges the pass attempt to Bridges (PHX).  Any ensuing contact is consider incidental.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Thompson's (GSW) pass attempt goes out of bounds.
Thompson (GSW) maintains a legal guarding position on Booker (PHX) during the drive and cleanly dislodges the ball.
Booker (PHX) clamps Thompson's (GSW) arm affecting his ability to retrieve the ball.
LLB shows Thompson (GSW) engages with Booker (PHX) during the screen but quickly disengages.
Booker (PHX) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of McKinnie (GSW) and firms up on his shoulder during the pick but he is able to move through contact.

Green (GSW) establishes his defensive position in Johnson's (PHX) path at the start of the drive.  Johnson briefly fumbles the ball prior to Green making marginal contact to his arm.   Johnson is able to regain control of his dribble.
Iguodala (GSW) has his arms extended away from his body when he goes for the ball and makes marginal contact to Ayton (PHX) as he secures the rebound.
McKinnie (GSW) briefly grasps Ayton's (PHX) side during the pick but does not affect his obtained position.
Green (GSW) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Bridges (PHX) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Johnson (PHX) makes contact with Iguodala's (GSW) arm during the rebound but does not affect his ability to retrieve the ball.
Johnson (PHX) places his arm to Green's (GSW) arm as he moves around the screen but he does not affect his FOM.
Bridges (PHX) makes some contact with McKinnie (GSW) during the rebound but does not affect his ability to retrieve the ball.
McKinnie (GSW) makes contact to Booker's (PHX) arm and loses control of the ball.
LLB shows Bridges (PHX) cleanly dislodges the ball from Curry (GSW).
Curry (GSW) makes contact to the arm of Bridges (PHX) that affects his SQBR.
